OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Flargely easing away this evening, but
OL,7,Fskies remaining cloudy. Locally heavy
OL,8,Frain across Northern Ireland and the
OL,9,Fnorthwest later in the night. A mild
OL,10,Fnight under the blanket of cloud with
OL,11,Fsome clearer spells in the east of
OL,12,FEngland.
