OL,14,CThursday:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,15,Frain across northwestern areas, drier
OL,16,Felsewhere with sunny spells developing
OL,17,Fin the south and slowly spreading
OL,18,Fnorth. Feeling warmer, especially in
OL,19,Fthe sunshine in the south.
